d their equals ( Section 3 No. 6 EStG) R 9 Severance payments due to termination of employment (Section 3 No. 9 EStG) R 10 Transitional payments, transitional grants (Section 3 No. 10 EStG) R 11 Aid and support given because of need (Section 3 No. 11 EStG) R 12 Aid from public funds for the purposes of education, training, research, science or art (Section 3 No. 11 and 44 EStG) R 13 Expense allowances from public funds (\u00a7 3 No. 12 EStG) R 14 Travel expenses, relocation allowances and separation allowances from public coffers (\u00a7 3 No. 13 EStG) R 14a"}, {"meta": {"name": "0115351.xml"}, "text": "Public funds R 15 Marriage allowances and childbirth allowances (Section 3 No. 15 EStG) R 16 Reimbursement of travel expenses, moving costs and additional expenses in the case of double housekeeping outside the public service (Section 3 No. 16 EStG) R 17 Expense allowances for part-time activities (Section 3 No. 26 EStG) R 18 Benefits according to the Part-Time Workers Act (Section 3 No. 28 EStG) R 19 Tool money (Section 3 No. 30 EStG) R 20 Provision of typical work clothing (Section 3 No. 31 EStG) R 21 Collective transport of employees between home and work (Section 3 No. 32 EStG ) R 21a"}, {"meta": {"name": "0115351.xml"}, "text": "Accommodation and care for children not required to attend school (Section 3 No. 33 EStG) R 21b"}, {"meta": {"name": "0115351.xml"}, "text": "Travel allowances (Section 3 No. 34 EStG) R 21c"}, {"meta": {"name": "0115351.xml"}, "text": "In addition to the wages owed anyway, R 21d"}, {"meta": {"name": "0115351.xml"}, "text": "Wages from marginal employment (Section 3 No. 39 EStG) R 22 Transit funds, reimbursement of expenses (Section 3 No. 50 EStG) R 23 R 23a"}, {"meta": {"name": "0115351.xml"}, "text": "Tax-free rental benefits (Section 3 No. 59) R 24 Future security benefits (Section 3 No. 62 EStG, Section 2 Paragraph 2 No. 3 LStDV) R 25R 26 Purchasing power compensation (Section 3 No. 64 EStG) R 27 Insolvency insurance (Section 3 No. 65